charges.charge_description: UNLAWFUL TRANSPORT OF FIREARMS, ETC. then being an alien illegally and unlawfully in the United States, knowingly did possess in and affecting commerce, firearms and ammunition, that is, a Savage .17 caliber rifle, an Interarms 25-06 rifle, a Hi Point .45 caliber handgun, a Smith &; Wesson .22 caliber handgun, .45 caliber ammunition, .22 caliber ammunition and 25-06 ammunition, all of which had been shipped and transported in interstate commerce; In violation of Title 18, United States Code, Sections 922(g)(5)(A), 924(a)(2) and 924(e)(1)
